sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Ingress as Platform Ingress<br/>Gateway API / kube-rbac-proxy
    participant HTTP as vllm-rocm HTTP API<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant GRPC as vllm-rocm gRPC API<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant Engine as vLLM Engine<br/>(PagedAttention)
    participant GPU as AMD ROCm GPU<br/>HIP/ROCm
    participant S3 as Model Storage<br/>S3 / PVC

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: Model Inference Request (HTTP)
    Client->>Ingress: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Auth: Platform-enforced
    Ingress->>HTTP: Forward Request<br/>(auth validated upstream)
    HTTP->>Engine: Inference Request
    Engine->>GPU: GPU Compute<br/>HIP/ROCm kernels
    GPU-->>Engine: Tensor Results
    Engine-->>HTTP: Completion Response
    HTTP-->>Ingress: JSON Response
    Ingress-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 1b: Model Inference Request (gRPC/TGIS)
    Client->>Ingress: gRPC GenerateStream<br/>Auth: Platform-enforced
    Ingress->>GRPC: Forward gRPC Request
    GRPC->>Engine: Inference Request
    Engine->>GPU: GPU Compute<br/>HIP/ROCm kernels
    GPU-->>Engine: Tensor Results
    Engine-->>GRPC: Streaming Response
    GRPC-->>Ingress: gRPC Stream
    Ingress-->>Client: gRPC Stream Response

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: Model Loading at Startup
    Engine->>S3: Download Model Weights<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+ (S3)<br/>or Filesystem (PVC)
    S3-->>Engine: Model Artifacts
    Engine->>GPU: Transfer Model Weights<br/>HIP/ROCm (host→device)
    Note over GPU: Model loaded into GPU memory
